id: pm-g9yi
title: Reject undefined placeholder IDs in parent/dependency inputs
description: "Dogfood run showed create accepted --parent undefined and --dep id=undefined, producing persisted references like parent=undefined and dependency id=pm-undefined instead of failing fast."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: external-audit,ids,pm-cli,validation
created_at: "2026-04-26T08:38:37.889Z"
