author: codex-agent
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: create/update reject undefined placeholder tokens for parent and dependency id fields with actionable guidance; regression tests cover both commands.
parent: pm-o7be
resolution: Reject placeholder tokens none/null/undefined for parent and dependency IDs in create/update paths.
expected_result: CLI rejects undefined placeholder IDs with actionable validation errors before persisting references.
actual_result: create/update now fail fast on undefined placeholder IDs and regression tests pass.
