  "2026-04-26T08:42:24.409Z",codex-agent,"Implemented validation guards in create/update parent+dependency parsing to reject undefined placeholder tokens; added regression coverage in create/update unit suites. Evidence: pnpm build passed and node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts passed (2 files, 77 tests)."
